download aspectJ from www.aspectj.org
install aspectJ (you need to have java installed)

to instrument your program use the aspectJ compiler, 
found under %aspectj-home%\bin

for example: 

ajc file.java SleepNoise.java

would create a new class file which includes the noise generated by SleepNoise
to run the class file you need to have aspectj libraries in you classpath
